---
---

<section id="itinerary" class="relative">
	<div class="bg-surface-container border border-outline-variant p-6 md:p-8 relative hud-border shadow-lg">
		<div class="hud-corner-tl"></div>
		<div class="hud-corner-tr"></div>
		<div class="hud-corner-bl"></div>
		<div class="hud-corner-br"></div>
		
		<div class="border-b border-outline-variant/50 pb-2 mb-8 flex justify-between items-center">
			<span class="font-label-caps text-neon-blue tracking-widest text-sm">
				<span class="lang-he">יומן תחנה: לוח זמנים של האירוע</span>
				<span class="lang-en">STATION LOG: EVENT SCHEDULE</span>
			</span>
			<span class="font-terminal-xs text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant opacity-60 uppercase hidden sm:inline">
				<span class="lang-he">מגזר רישום יומן WY-31</span>
				<span class="lang-en">LOGGING SECTOR WY-31</span>
			</span>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Itinerary Timeline Grid -->
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 font-terminal-xs">
			
			<!-- Item 1 -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-12 gap-3 p-4 border border-outline-variant/30 bg-black/20 hover:bg-neon-blue/5 hover:border-neon-blue/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
				<div class="sm:col-span-2 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-neon-blue text-sm group-hover:animate-pulse">login</span>
					<span class="text-secondary font-bold text-base">19:30</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<span class="text-white font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
						<span class="lang-he">הבסיס נפתח למבקרים</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Base Opens for Visitors</span>
					</span>
					<span class="text-[10px] text-hazard-orange tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5">
						<span class="lang-he">נקודת ביקורת מאובטחת 31</span>
						<span class="lang-en">SECURE CHECKPOINT 31</span>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-6 flex items-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
						<span class="lang-he">צ'ק-אין מהיר והתאקלמות. תופסים מחסה מהסופה שבחוץ. בירה קרה ומשקאות יחכו לכם בבר כדי להפשיר את הקור.</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Rapid check-in and acclimation. Taking shelter from the blizzard outside. Cold beer and hot drinks await at the bar to thaw you out.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Item 2 -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-12 gap-3 p-4 border border-outline-variant/30 bg-black/20 hover:bg-neon-blue/5 hover:border-neon-blue/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
				<div class="sm:col-span-2 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-neon-blue text-sm group-hover:animate-pulse">movie</span>
					<span class="text-secondary font-bold text-base">20:00</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<span class="text-white font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
						<span class="lang-he">הקרנת THE THING</span>
						<span class="lang-en">The Thing Screening</span>
					</span>
					<span class="text-[10px] text-hazard-orange tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5">
						<span class="lang-he">הקרנה על מסך 150 אינץ׳</span>
						<span class="lang-en">150" PROJECTION SCREEN</span>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-6 flex items-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
						<span class="lang-he">כיבוי אורות. הקרנה של יצירת המופת הקלאסית של ג'ון קרפנטר משנת 1982 (109 דקות). Dolby Surround Activated – הסאונד עוטף, האולם חשוך, אין דרך חזרה.</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Lights out. Screening of John Carpenter's 1982 classic masterpiece (109 mins). Dolby Surround Activated – the sound envelops you, the room goes black, there is no turning back.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Item 3 -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-12 gap-3 p-4 border border-outline-variant/30 bg-black/20 hover:bg-neon-blue/5 hover:border-neon-blue/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
				<div class="sm:col-span-2 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-neon-blue text-sm group-hover:animate-pulse">forum</span>
					<span class="text-secondary font-bold text-base">21:45</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<span class="text-white font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
						<span class="lang-he">הרצאה טכנית ושאלות ותשובות</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Technical Lecture & Q&A</span>
					</span>
					<span class="text-[10px] text-hazard-orange tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5">
						<span class="lang-he">הרצאת עומק</span>
						<span class="lang-en">IN-DEPTH LECTURE</span>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-6 flex items-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
						<span class="lang-he">חגי יניב צולל להרצאת עומק על יצירת המופת של ג'ון קרפנטר. נחשוף את סודות ההפקה שמאחורי הקלעים, ננתח את העשייה הייחודית ונגלה מה הופך את הסרט הזה לנכס צאן ברזל קולנועי. בסיום: שאלות ותשובות עם הקהל, כל עוד אנחנו עדיין בטוחים...</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Haggai Yaniv dives deep into John Carpenter's masterpiece. We will uncover behind-the-scenes production secrets, analyze the unique craftsmanship, and discover what makes this film a cinematic staple. Ending with a Q&A session, as long as we're still safe...</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Item 4 -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-12 gap-3 p-4 border border-outline-variant/30 bg-black/20 hover:bg-neon-blue/5 hover:border-neon-blue/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
				<div class="sm:col-span-2 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-neon-blue text-sm group-hover:animate-pulse">logout</span>
					<span class="text-secondary font-bold text-base">22:30</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<span class="text-white font-bold tracking-wide uppercase">
						<span class="lang-he">שחרור לחץ באאוטפוסט</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Post-Event Decompression</span>
					</span>
					<span class="text-[10px] text-hazard-orange tracking-widest uppercase mt-0.5">
						<span class="lang-he">מפגש חברתי בבר</span>
						<span class="lang-en">SOCIAL GATHERING AT THE BAR</span>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="sm:col-span-6 flex items-center rtl:text-right ltr:text-left">
					<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
						<span class="lang-he">טיהור הבסיס וסגירת שערים. בירה קרה ומשקאות קלים יחולקו לשורדים. בדיקת דם סופית לזיהוי הדבקה לפני פינוי.</span>
						<span class="lang-en">Base decontamination and gate closing. Cold beer and soft drinks for survivors. Final blood testing for infection checks before evacuation.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>
